ttle, Portland, and Minneapolis; in 2014 they will hit the Southwest.&nbsp;</p>
<p><br />In the last year Sound Alliance has performed with Eric Marienthal, Conrad Herwig, Ed Calle, Ingrid Jensen, with Delfaeyo Marsalis scheduled for February 2013. We have a strong program of bringing in renowned guest for master classes and performances, often with students. Students have the opportunity to "jam" with the jazz faculty every Wednesday night at Sammy's, a local club two blocks from the music building with a cozy environment, great acoustics, and the best burgers and shakes around. <br /><br />The Department of Music offers a Bachelor of Music degree in Jazz Studies with full and adjunct faculty for every jazz instrument, a Jazz Society, and opportunity to get off campus; we're going to the Lionel Hampton Jazz Festival again in February. Scholarships are available through the instruments areas (saxophone, trumpet, and trombone) and jazz specific awards for rhythm instrument players. <br /><br />We <a href="x46634.xml" title="Jazz Auditions">audition</a> every semester for our ensembles and encourage you to join us!</p>]]></BodyCopy><xPower Type="GroupStart" GroupStart="" Name="PageComponents" label="Page Components" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="true"><xPower Type="List" List="xpowercomponent_Optional" Name="OptionalColumnComponent" label="Optional Column Components" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="" CompTypes="FacebookComponent;Image;ColumnTextComponent;Media;Quote" Expanded="true"><xPower Type="Component" Component="x46434" Name="Optional" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="FacebookComponent;Image;ColumnTextComponent;Media;Quote" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="x46436" Name="Optional" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="FacebookComponent;Image;ColumnTextComponent;Media;Quote" Expanded="false"/></xPower><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="QuickLinksColumn1" label="QuickLinks Column 1" readonly="false" hidden="fa